right to death on demand to refer terminally ill members to a 
center he wanted to open in california founder and executive 
director derek humphry said 
i persuaded him not to take up in california humphry said 
from the netherlands where he was presiding over an international 
convention on righttodie issues we didnt want to be involved 
in lawbreaking 
