association was kidnapped on sept 5 1977 when two of his 
bodyguards were cut down in a hail of bullets on a cologne street 
he was held by the red army faction for six weeks before being 
slain 
the red army faction a spinoff of the baadermeinhof gang got 
its start with a series of arson and bombing attacks mainly against 
us military targets in what it said was retaliation for the war 
in vietnam 
it later broadened its attacks staging bombings and slayings of 
west german industrial and banking leaders 
