sympathizers who provide hideouts and other support for gang members 
the latest attack claimed by the red army faction was bombing 
death of banker alfred herrhausen on nov 30 herrhausen 59 was 
head of deutsche bank west germanys largest commercial bank he 
was killed when a bomb was detonated under his armored car as he was 
being driven to work from his home in bad homburg 12 miles north of 
frankfurt 
in october 1977 a group of palestinian terrorists hijacked a 
lufthansa plane to mogadishu somalia and demanded the release of 
jailed terrorists belonging to the baadermeinhof group 
the hijackers were overpowered by a west german antiterrorist 
unit on oct 18 1977 after the plane landed in mogadishu 
