secret ballot said anna generalova a church spokeswoman 
alexi 61 takes the helm of the church at a time when decades of 
soviet government repression are being lifted and interest in 
religion is growing 
a church council of 330 members chose him as successor to 
patriarch pimen who died may 3 at age 79 
he won despite predictions that many would consider him an 
inappropriate leader because he is of baltic rather than russian 
descent 
