firm kohlberg kravis roberts amp co which bought the company then 
a huge foods and consumer products conglomerate in a 61 billion 
leveraged buyout in 1986 
since then beatrice has sold off most of its businesses but 
still retains such wellknown food brands as hunts wesson 
manwich peter pan snack pak swiss miss la choy swift premium 
butterball eckrich and reddiwip 
